-- // Created by StarWars local Debris = game:GetService("Debris")
local GearService = require(1075123174)
local tool = script.Parent local handle = tool.Handle local wandModel = tool.Wand local particlesFolder = tool.Particles
local rand = Random.new()
local gear = GearService:BindGear(tool) gear:SetupRemoteFunctions() gear:SetupLocalScript("MouseIcon")
local TIMEOUT = 10 local RELOAD_TIME = 2 local SPELL_SPEED = 24 local DAMAGE = 15
handle.Transparency = 1 for _, obj in pairs(wandModel:GetDescendants()) do if obj:IsA("BasePart") then obj.Transparency = 0 end end
function InvokeClient(mode, value) if gear.Player and mode then local result pcall(function() result = gear.ClientControls:InvokeClient(gear.Player, mode, value) end)
return result end end
function CreateSpell() local newPart = Instance.new("Part") local particle = particlesFolder:GetChildren()[rand:NextInteger(1, #particlesFolder:GetChildren())]:Clone()
newPart.Size = Vector3.new(1, 1, 1) newPart.Transparency = 1 newPart.CanCollide = false newPart.Touched:Connect(function(hit) if hit:IsDescendantOf(gear.Character) then return end local parentTo = hit.Parent if parentTo then if parentTo:IsA("Accessory") or parentTo:IsA("Tool") then parentTo = parentTo.Parent end
local humanoid = parentTo:FindFirstChildOfClass("Humanoid") if humanoid then humanoid:TakeDamage(DAMAGE) end end
newPart:Destroy() end)
local bodyVelocity = Instance.new("BodyVelocity", newPart) bodyVelocity.MaxForce = Vector3.new(5000, 5000, 5000)
local bodyForce = Instance.new("BodyForce", newPart) bodyForce.Force = Vector3.new(0, newPart:GetMass() * workspace.Gravity, 0)
particle.Parent = newPart
return {Part = newPart, BodyVelocity = bodyVelocity, Particle = particle} end
tool.Activated:Connect(function() if not tool.Enabled or not gear:IsPlayerAlive() then return end tool.Enabled = false
local mouseData = InvokeClient("GetMouseData") if mouseData then local direction = (mouseData.Position - gear.RootPart.CFrame.p).Unit local newSpell = CreateSpell() newSpell.Part.CFrame = CFrame.new(gear.RootPart.CFrame.p) newSpell.BodyVelocity.Velocity = direction * SPELL_SPEED newSpell.Part.Parent = workspace newSpell.Particle.Enabled = true
Debris:AddItem(newSpell.Part, TIMEOUT) end
wait(RELOAD_TIME) tool.Enabled = true end)

-- // Created by StarWars local RunService = game:GetService("RunService")
local tool = script.Parent local wandMotorsFolder = tool:WaitForChild("WandMotors")
local count = 0
local SPEED = 10
RunService.Stepped:Connect(function(_, step) for _, motor in pairs(wandMotorsFolder:GetChildren()) do if motor:IsA("Motor6D") then motor.Transform = motor.Transform * CFrame.Angles(0, 0, math.rad(count)) end end count = (count + (step * SPEED)) % 360 end)
